  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Speaker assures international diplomats that presidential election will be held transparently",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardhana told the ambassadors and high commissioners that all arrangements have been made to carry out the process of electing a new president transparently as the oldest country in Asia.",
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sung, EU Ambassador Denis Saipi, New Zealand High Commissioner Michelle Apelton, British High Commissioner Sarah Halton, Australian High Commissioner David Holley and Canadian High Commissioner David McGinnon attended the meeting held at the Parliament building.",
        "As the oldest country in Asia with a secure parliamentary democracy, Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena informed the delegates and ambassadors that all arrangements have been made to carry out the process of electing a new president in a transparent manner.",
        "The Secretary General of the Parliament explained to the Ambassadors and High Commissioners the process of electing the new President through the Parliament. The Ambassadors and High Commissioners appreciated the steps taken to ensure democracy in the country."
      ],
